title: Bug 116564: The title of hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options", now it changes with settings.
OB: When opening the hyperlink builder, the title is incorrect and changes with the settings.
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options", but currently it changes with the settings.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Click on "OK" in the hyperlink builder.
2. Reopen the hyperlink builder.

Actual result: The title of the hyperlink builder becomes "www.actuate.com".

Expected result: The title of the hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options".
